Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.25,0:02:06.62,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,Let us destroy one another
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.62,0:02:09.79,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,And face the ending full of mystery that lies ahead
